Output docs/orc-v3-rust-demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1500
Set Height 900
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Type "python3 tools/seed_v3_demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "env -u NO_COLOR ORC_HOME=/tmp/orc-v3-demo rust/target/release/orc top"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 700ms
Down
Enter
Sleep 2s
Tab
Sleep 1s
Tab
Sleep 1s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
